# Portfolio website
Vibe-coded portfolio website.

Design system used: https://www.designmd.co/d/bmw

## Prompt used

Convert LinkedIn Profile PDF -> Profile.md
```
Profile.pdf Turn this into md file
```

For Google Stitch:
```
Create a design system using the file [bmw-DESIGN.md].


Create 1 page portfolio website for [Profile.md]
```

In Antigravity:
Create more pages from code:
```
Build [project list HTML page], same design as [Google Stitch Zip Export] 
```
